Class FaceNetNN4Small2

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.zoo.ZooModel
      • org.deeplearning4j.zoo.model.FaceNetNN4Small2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InstantiableModel

    public class FaceNetNN4Small2
extends ZooModel
    A variant of the original FaceNet model that relies on embeddings and triplet loss. Reference: https://arxiv.org/abs/1503.03832 Also based on the OpenFace implementation: http://reports-archive.adm.cs.cmu.edu/anon/2016/CMU-CS-16-118.pdf Revised and consolidated version by @crockpotveggies
